### **Business Consulting / Change Management Stream**

**Reference Number:** cb-688-46607899
**Tender Closing Date:** 2024-02-08 18:00:00

**Summary:**

Environment and Climate Change Canada is seeking the services of a change management consultant and a facilitator consultant to support project management and implement meetings and workshops in the Vancouver Metropolitan Area. The contract is intended to result in the award of one (1) contract.

**Category:** 2. Business Consulting / Change Management Stream

**Work Streams:**

* 2.6 Change Management Consultant
* 2.15 Facilitator Consultant

**Regional Requirements:**

* The contract is limited to the Vancouver Metropolitan Area.

**Security Requirement:**

* There is no security requirement associated with this contract.

**Trade Agreements:**

* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement

**Contract Period and Level of Effort:**

* The contract is for a period of one year, from 2024-03-01 to 2025-04-15.
* The estimated level of effort is 750 hours.

**Requirements:**

* The contractors are expected to provide professional services as change management consultants and facilitator consultants to support project management and implement meetings and workshops.
* The contractors must be able to demonstrate a high level of expertise in the area of change management and facilitation.

**Eligibility:**

* The contract is open only to Supply Arrangement Holders under E60ZT-18TSPS who qualified under Tier 1 and under the stated consultant category.

**Solicitation Documents:**

* None

**Notice and Timeline:**

* The notice was published on 2024-01-24 and will close on 2024-02-08 18:00:00.
* The expected contract start date is 2024-03-01.

**Contact Information:**

* Heidi Noble: Heidi.Noble@ec.gc.ca
* (289) 348-2015

**Related Files:**

* The full notice is available at [https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/30306/npp_5000071245r_fr.pdf](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/30306/npp_5000071245r_fr.pdf). ## Attachments
